Additionally, the paper may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category as federated learning is a popular technique in AI research. The paper may also be relevant to the distributed computing (cs.DC) sub-category as it involves communication between multiple devices. The systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category may also be relevant as the paper discusses communication complexity guarantees. Finally, the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category may be relevant as federated learning is often used in image and video analysis tasks.
